text: Toysa Nabiyow Yallih gital Qeb abaay ingicilliy kay Qangara fayya ittam keh, ku-Rabbi kok-sa kah amrise mara malik munaafiqhiin kok abta Raq maxaagitin, Nabiyow moominiin Qeebih ilsiisaay ken kah Sangeelis Yalli koroositeh yan marih Qeb kee gibda koo kee moominiinik waaselek Yalli Qandeh kulliimik gibdiih kay digaala korosul gibiduk Raqta
